{"tid":800071,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【極經典仿官慢服】源．墨香Online ;有冇人一齊玩","createTime":"2018-08-30T14:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T09:44:48.000Z","uid":78763,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"439d0ac24415d6ad50a3ac4a6d26dac47cc72ed7","tid":800071,"uid":78763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T14:39:11.000Z","msg":"copy &amp; paste <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全球唯一還原度最高'最公平公正的極經典仿官慢服版本<br />\n支援繁簡雙語系統，強勢打造十二年前玩法<br />\n堅持最經典原味，最公平墨香，惜日戰友 江湖重聚<br />\n保留在線商城泡點系統，不讓課金玩家獨大<br />\n廢除自動狩獵系統，重回最初的感覺<br />\n<br />\n官方網站：<a href=\"http://sjmso.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsjmso.com%2F&d=NQRpmiJNK76EDsQIlzutQXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=50f948fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sjmso.com/</a><br />\n官方專頁：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yuanmso/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyuanmso%2F&d=NQRpmiJNK76EDsQIlzutQXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=3aae14e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yuanmso/</a><br />\n代理微信：yuanmsoKF<br />\n<br />\n【在線泡點設置】<br />\n所有地圖每10分鐘獲得20泡點<br />\n蘭州地圖每10分鐘獲得25泡點<br />\n<br />\n【本服設置】<br />\n經驗值：5倍<br />\n技能點：25倍<br />\n金錢率：10倍<br />\n掉寶率：10倍<br />\n武功技能：從7層開始 ( 第11層100% 需到演武場升級至12層 )<br />\n等級上限：99<br />\n<br />\n【祝福石設置】<br />\n武器祝福值：攻擊(1~10)，生命、護體、內力(10~100)<br />\n防具類:生命護體 內力(25-250) 防禦力(1-20) 五行屬性(1-10)<br />\n首飾類:力量、敏捷、心脈、體力(1-5)<br />\n<br />\n【本服優點】<br />\n頂端線路，不受任何攻擊，環境暢順<br />\n市面上唯一一隻最接近2006年的墨香版本<br />\n仿官方服，沒有所謂新技能，打造十年前玩法<br />\n獨家24小時活動制，長期在線的玩家不怕悶<br />\n設有遊戲端源碼，只要你提出我們皆能實現，打造最獨家的墨香<br />\n廢取自動狩獵，回味最初人手升級的感覺<br />\n設有在線 元寶、泡點 商城，不讓課金玩家獨大<br />\n<br />\n【開服宗旨】<br />\n開發過程與完成品確定無BUG無錯誤以「品質」為核心打造更好「品牌」<br />\n用心為所有玩家服務、對任何玩家都絕對一視同仁<br />\n追求永續經營為理念、打造最接近2006年的墨香<br />\n<br />\n★豐富活動，GM將會在線和玩家進行不同活動，豐富獎勵等著你！<br />\n★定期舉辦武林大會，勝出者除了有名聲，還有豐富獎品！<br />\n★每星期舉辦活動讓玩家玩個不停，想獲免費也能稱霸就不能錯過！<br />\n★遊戲內其它特色無法在此逐個列出，讓大家在遊戲中慢慢享受。<br />\n<br />\n～趕快加入吧！承諾永久終生開放～<br />\n<br />\n利申:非打手 一直搵緊墨香玩，有冇人一齊玩 個spec好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望唔好又死城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4073e70725d68422141337f70b52545951bf96b","tid":800071,"uid":78763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5bce359f7fd5354a1114c4522187c4fdb738c5c","tid":800071,"uid":21153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:02:52.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"87749707a646cf9cdfaeed75870bea7cf1784294","tid":800071,"uid":78763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5bce359f7fd5354a1114c4522187c4fdb738c5c","tid":800071,"uid":21153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:02:52.000Z","msg":"LM"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:06:27.000Z","msg":"手動慢服你都岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我打算玩槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a54ba6416653ed2ae4b9524ea93a70c88c5a589","tid":800071,"uid":78763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5bce359f7fd5354a1114c4522187c4fdb738c5c","tid":800071,"uid":21153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:02:52.000Z","msg":"LM"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:06:47.000Z","msg":"烏龍 啪啪啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492970790915047fbbdaaadfd6530d8390570933","tid":800071,"uid":21153,"like":0,"dislike"